                            <property name="can-focus">False</property>
                            <property name="label" translatable="yes" context="regexbuilder|example_caution">Performance tip
Prefer bounded quantifiers and specific character classes. Avoid deeply nested ambiguous repetitions such as (.*)+. LibreOffice limits regex execution, but a simpler pattern is easier to review and reuse.</property>
